In this study, we introduced the chamber pressure as a parameter for controlling the methylammonium iodide (MAI) evaporation and respective impingement rate during the growth of methylammonium lead iodide (MAPbI3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
