				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$_2$$\end{document} flux of 0.2 Å/s, we found an optimum chamber pressure for MAI deposition at 7.5 ×\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
